sentences: Julia Shammas Holter (born December 18, 1984) is an American singer-songwriter, record producer, composer and artist, based in Los Angeles.
Following three independent album productions, Holter released Tragedy as her first official studio album in 2011.
Ekstasis, followed in 2012.
After signing with Domino Records in 2013, she released the albums Loud City Song (2013), Have You in My Wilderness (2015) and the live-in-the-studio album In the Same Room (2017).
